00:39:40.360 --> 00:39:43.510
Complete nonsense.

00:39:43.510 --> 00:39:48.790
For Beethoven, this was "Sonata
Quasi una Fantasia," "Sonata

00:39:48.790 --> 00:39:51.880
in the Form of a Dream."

00:39:51.880 --> 00:39:57.476
