00:40:52.650 --> 00:40:53.980
And so on and so forth.

00:40:53.980 --> 00:40:55.620
Now, I am doing that.

00:40:55.620 --> 00:40:56.779
So the voices are there.

00:40:56.779 --> 00:40:58.320
And I can tell you,
