It's--

00:41:22.600 --> 00:41:23.600
[GENTLE PIANO PLAYING]

00:41:23.600 --> 00:41:26.020
--the evenness, the
complete evenness,

00:41:26.020 --> 00:41:27.750
and the color, and
then the voices.

00:41:30.360 --> 00:41:34.110
So all that is going on,
